==English==
===Etymology===
[[blend|Blend]] of [[trust fund]] and [[Rastafarian]]
[[Category:Portmanteaus]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

#''Trustafarian'' is a derogatory portmanteau made up from the words ''trust fund'' and ''Rastafarian''. It is used to degrade some white people who allegedly adopt the manners of [[Rastafari]]; in other circumstances they might be called ''[[wigger]]s''. They are people, often young to middle aged, who are said to fuse the fashion sensibilities of a hippie with those of a Rastafarian. They are often assumed by their detractors to live an unemployed, shiftless life of hedonism based on an unlimited amount of funds (a trust fund). In some cases, they are believed to adhere to the [[Ital]] dietary principles of Rastafari. 

